{"tid":639195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入票站先知「被投票」 彭小姐嘆變廢票權利被剝削","createTime":"2018-04-23T09:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T17:27:28.000Z","uid":92301,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c997ee5ab3ff3aba97e144b3a981de774718dc91","tid":639195,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:50:28.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》接獲新界東選民彭小姐投訴稱，今天在票站登記準備投票時，票站職員卻指記錄顯示她早已投票，懷疑遭人冒認或記錄出錯。即使票站選舉主任容許彭小姐重新投票，但其一票已慘變廢票。彭小姐不滿選舉事務處馬虎了事，變相剝奪其投票權利，要求處方加強票站監督。<br />\n<br />\n彭小姐今天下午到西貢市中心大會堂票站投票，然而身份證號碼記錄上早已劃線標示她早已投票，票站職員反問她「今朝有冇去過(投票)？」其後選舉主任對她表示，通常此情況或因票站職員出錯，亦可能是「有啲公公婆婆朝早嚟咗投，下晝又嚟投過」。彭小組對主任的言論感奇怪，強調「我冇嚟過...駛唔駛叫警察證明？」主任表示信任彭小姐，著她重新投票。經她再三查問，主任才承認此票將會成為「廢票」，並放入標示「重複投票」的信封另行處理。彭遂即場作書面投訴。<br />\n<br />\n彭小姐促處方查證她是否遭人刻意冒認，還是有職員出錯，並檢討查證及監督程序。她又呼籲其他選民，若有同一遭遇必須向票站職員追究到底，「千祈唔好聽佢講息事寧人，要主動追落去要佢交代」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160228/54809529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160228%2F54809529&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=b201b55f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160228%2F54809529&h=e290dea0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160228/54809529</a>"},{"pid":"79ea1b65860272f2dc5fa42c48d96c88542ca838","tid":639195,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T16:51:31.000Z","msg":"old news is so exciting to review<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3681e474ae160a43c30548ead900251da202502f","tid":639195,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"其實可以每人出一張有自己個人資料既投票通知書(好似銀紙咁加埋防偽特徵)<br />\n投票要帶埋去，<br />\n憑通知書加身份證拎票，<br />\n應該可以解決問題？"},{"pid":"44f7c8ddb81980dc913891ab6804c811fd78c858","tid":639195,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3681e474ae160a43c30548ead900251da202502f","tid":639195,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"其實可以每人出一張有自己個人資料既投票通知書(好似銀紙咁加埋防偽特徵)<br />\n投票要帶埋去，<br />\n憑通知書加身份證拎票，<br />\n應該可以解決問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"環保撚會全力阻止"},{"pid":"9f3f384431c9c18ff6351b15feff2b6140a8eeeb","tid":639195,"uid":58851,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"咁多人做嘢, 實有人出錯<br />\n但政府D人處理手法就係掩飾問題"},{"pid":"a29d4a47d04ce2104f8c0a390ba9e534c3f08a7b","tid":639195,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"She was given a tendered ballot paper in this case. The UK also operates a similar system - <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2011/1/schedule/2/part/1/chapter/4/crossheading/tendered-ballot-papers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.uk%2Fukpga%2F2011%2F1%2Fschedule%2F2%2Fpart%2F1%2Fchapter%2F4%2Fcrossheading%2Ftendered-ballot-papers&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=f8c00623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2011/1/schedule/2/part/1/chapter/4/crossheading/tendered-ballot-papers</a>"}]}